childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Deku Tree...^$1Dodongo's Cavern...^$2Link's Pocket...^$iYe who may become a Hero...&Offer the spiritual stones and&play the Song of Time.

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Fire Temple...^$3Shadow Temple...^$4Forest Temple...^$5Water Temple...^$6Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$7Spirit Temple...^$lThe awakened ones require&the Shadow and Spirit Medallions&as well as the Light Arrows.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be kept in a big chest&%rinside its tower%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...
